<topic id='attribute_referred_out_of_area_reason_for_adult_acute_mental_health.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: REFERRED OUT OF AREA REASON FOR ADULT ACUTE MENTAL HEALTH - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
The reason a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>:        </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>with assessed acute mental health needs and</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>
requiring adult mental health admitted 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 care                    </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
was referred to an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>:        </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>
that does not form part of the referring 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>'s usual local network of 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>
 and                    </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>
where the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_mental_health_care_coordinator">Mental Health Care Coordinator</xref>
 cannot visit the 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 as often as stated in the referring 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>'s policy.                    </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
For further information, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>
 part of the gov.uk website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/oaps-in-mental-health-services-for-adults-in-acute-inpatient-care" scope="external" format="html">Out of area placements in mental health services for adults in acute inpatient care</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
</body>
